column1: #Text=Ksenia Sukhinova of Russia , won the Miss World 2008 crown on Saturday , outshining 108 other international competitors .
#Text=She was crowned by her predecessor Miss World 2007 , Zhang Zilin of the People 's Republic of China .
#Text=She pledged to " help people " and said , " I think I can help people and I want to help people and today if I walk away with this crown I will do that . "
#Text=Sukhinova , 5 ' 10 " , said that her immediate ambitions included meeting Russia 's president Dmitry Medvedev .
